rage.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"screen\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"Zonewill\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"the live feed\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific event\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"theGold Zonecoverage\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock Live Actions will also allow viewers watching the NBC Primetime simulcast to add upcoming events to their \\\"My Stuff\\\" list to watch later.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2261, \"end\": 2268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.769111267166681e-13, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}, {\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9995770032678465, \"rank\": 0.000423056549033983, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"upcoming events\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"My Stuff\\\" list\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock Discovery Multiview With up to 40 live events happening simultaneously, Peacock Discovery Multiview will offer an industry-first, enhanced four-view experience that helps users navigate to the most important events, with real-time on-screen descriptions from NBCU's Olympic experts informing viewers about what is at stake, such as a medal event, an elimination risk or a first-time Olympian.\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2415, \"title\": \"htt