round the screens, switch the audio and click through to watch full screen and dive deeper into the action.\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2981, \"end\": 2990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Multiview\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"users\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"the screens\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"the audio\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"full screen\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will offer up to four Multiview options concurrently, giving fans the opportunity to choose what they are most excited to watch.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3163, \"end\": 3172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Multiview\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will be the first standalone streaming app to offer a Multiview experience across smart TVs, streaming devices, web browsers and tablets.\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3333, \"end\": 3342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amiga_support_and_maintenance_software\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Multiview\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpe